//--------------------------------------------------Allure Report Documentation-----------------------------------------------------------//
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Steps to Generate Allure Report
-------------------------------
1.Download allure command line tools(.zip)
link : "https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/io/qameta/allure/allure-commandline/2.8.0/"

2.Download apache maven (.zip) 
link: "https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi"

3.Copy the Bin folder path of both command line tools and apache maven
and paste to to the path in system environment variables path.

4.After Step 3 check the maven version by 'mvn--version' command

5.After Setting up the Alure Frame work Run the Testng Test

6.After Execution of the TestNg Test open the Command Prompt and type "Allure Serve"

7.Step 6 will generate the report and open in the browser 